Package: sherpa.onnx
Type: Package
Title: Speech Recognition with Sherpa-ONNX
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides offline speech recognition (audio file to text transcription)
    using the sherpa-onnx library. Features automatic model downloads from HuggingFace
    Hub, support for multiple model architectures (Whisper, Paraformer, SenseVoice),
    Voice Activity Detection (VAD) for processing long audio files, and efficient
    batch processing through an R6 class interface.
License: Apache License (>= 2.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    R6 (>= 2.5.0),
    rappdirs (>= 0.3.0),
    hfhub (>= 0.1.0),
    tibble (>= 3.0.0)
LinkingTo:
    cpp11 (>= 0.4.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
SystemRequirements: C++17
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
